Interface PaAttributeValuePortFilterBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaAttributeValuePortFilterBuilderIetf

    public interface PaAttributeValuePortFilterBuilder
extends ImAttributeValueBuilder
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement port filter attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
